<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8255093>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Habitus and morphological features of Micronecta poweri (Douglas & Scott, 1869), male, A. dorsal view, B. median lobe of sternum VII, C. prestrigilar flap, D. free lobe of tergum VIII, E. left paramere, F. right paramere. Scale for A= 0.5 mm, B–F= 0.1 mm." ;
